video.title: Power Rangers in Space
video.synopsis: With the Power Chamber destroyed, former Turbo Power Rangers T.J., Cassie, Carlos and Ashley search for Zordon, who's been abducted by Dark Specter.

episodes.synopsis: The Rangers and Alpha 6 are sucked into an unknown high-tech space ship. Meanwhile, Dark Specter assembles many of the universe's most evil villains.
episodes.title: From Out of Nowhere: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: With Astronema's forces closing in, the Red Ranger reveals his identity to the Rangers and presents them with new powers.
episodes.title: From Out of Nowhere: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: The Power Rangers return home to an explosive welcome on Earth from Ecliptor and Astronema.
episodes.title: Save Our Ship

episodes.synopsis: The Space Rangers meet the Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles.
episodes.title: Shell Shocked

episodes.synopsis: Andros returns to his home planet, KO-35, in search of his long-lost sister.
episodes.title: Never Stop Searching

episodes.synopsis: NASADA asks the Rangers to help retrieve a crashed satellite with important data on Dark Specter's operations.
episodes.title: Satellite Search

episodes.synopsis: While the Rangers are busy taking a test in school, Andros gets mixed up with a gang of car thieves.
episodes.title: A Ranger Among Thieves

episodes.synopsis: Cassie is trapped in a building under attack by Astronema's forces.
episodes.title: When Push Comes to Shove

episodes.synopsis: A malfunction with the Megaship's Simudeck releases hundreds of real Craterites into Angel Grove.
episodes.title: The Craterite Invasion

episodes.synopsis: Waspicable, a kind-hearted monster from Earth, is torn between his caring nature and his loyalty to his evil brother, Sting King.
episodes.title: The Wasp with a Heart

episodes.synopsis: The Phantom Ranger discovers where Dark Specter is hiding Zordon.
episodes.title: The Delta Discovery

episodes.synopsis: Professor Phenomenus develops a ray that can turn objects evil, which Astronema decides to use against the Power Rangers.
episodes.title: The Great Evilyzer

episodes.synopsis: Ashley's grandmother visits Angel Grove, intent on seeing Ashley engaged before she leaves.
episodes.title: Grandma Matchmaker

episodes.synopsis: A suspicious bounty hunter joins forces with Astronema despite Ecliptor's objections.
episodes.title: The Barillian Sting

episodes.synopsis: Darkonda betrays Ecliptor to increase his own power. Meanwhile, T.J. suffers an injury that causes him to lose his memory.
episodes.title: TJ's Identity Crisis

episodes.synopsis: Andros makes a startling discovery about his sister's kidnapper and journeys into the heart of Dark Specter's empire searching for answers.
episodes.title: Flashes of Darkonda

episodes.synopsis: The Power Rangers use their newly obtained Key Cards to decode the location of a new fleet of Zords.
episodes.title: The Rangers' Mega Voyage

episodes.synopsis: Justin, the Blue Turbo Ranger, returns to help the Power Rangers.
episodes.title: True Blue to the Rescue

episodes.synopsis: Astronema switches bodies with Ashley to infiltrate the Astro Megaship and capture the Power Rangers.
episodes.title: Invasion of the Body Switcher

episodes.synopsis: The Rangers discover the cryogenically frozen Silver Ranger, Zhane, who is Andros's best friend.
episodes.title: Survival of the Silver

episodes.synopsis: Andros battles Darkonda and his own jealousy as he worries Ashley might be attracted to Zhane.
episodes.title: Red with Envy

episodes.synopsis: After being frozen for two years, Zhane struggles with his weakening Ranger powers.
episodes.title: The Silver Secret

episodes.synopsis: Zhane struggles between his attraction to Astronema and his duty to help the other Power Rangers.
episodes.title: A Date with Danger

episodes.synopsis: The Rangers are captured on a desolate planet by a band of resistance fighters, prompting Zhane to reconsider his place with the Power Rangers.
episodes.title: Zhane's Destiny

episodes.synopsis: After accidentally hurting Cassie in battle, Carlos finds his self-confidence shaken, prompting an old Mighty Morphin friend to lend a hand.
episodes.title: Always a Chance

episodes.synopsis: When Darkonda sets a trap for the Red Ranger, Andros finally comes face-to-face with his long-lost sister.
episodes.title: The Secret of the Locket

episodes.synopsis: Astronema questions her own motives as she travels to KO-35 to battle the Power Rangers.
episodes.title: Astronema Thinks Twice

episodes.synopsis: The Power Rangers question whether they can trust Astronema when she offers to help them find Zordon.
episodes.title: The Rangers' Leap of Faith

episodes.synopsis: With a new ally aboard the Megaship, the Rangers race to save the Earth from an asteroid on a collision course with the planet.
episodes.title: Dark Specter's Revenge: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: An old ally returns to help Andros rescue his sister from Dark Specter.
episodes.title: Dark Specter's Revenge: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Astronema assembles a team of evil Psycho Rangers to solidify her power.
episodes.title: Rangers Gone Psycho

episodes.synopsis: Carlos must appease a little girl's every whim to keep his identity a secret.
episodes.title: Carlos On Call

episodes.synopsis: The Psycho Rangers take advantage of the animosity between the Ranger girls to capture Ashley.
episodes.title: A Rift in the Rangers

episodes.synopsis: T.J. devises a clever strategy to defeat the Psycho Rangers in battle.
episodes.title: Five of a Kind

episodes.synopsis: Able to recognize the Power Rangers' voices, the Psycho Rangers assume human disguises to try and find them when they least suspect it.
episodes.title: Silence Is Golden

episodes.synopsis: While searching for their Mega Voyager, the Power Rangers prepare for a final showdown with the Psycho Rangers.
episodes.title: The Enemy Within

episodes.synopsis: On a remote planet, Andros befriends a rapidly growing baby alien on the run from his cruel master.
episodes.title: Andros and the Stowaway

episodes.synopsis: Andros and Carlos are trapped inside Astronema's Secret City, forcing Andros to discover untapped powers in his Astro Morpher to save the day.
episodes.title: Mission to Secret City

episodes.synopsis: The Rangers race to stop Astronema from using her new device to turn people into Data Cards.
episodes.title: Ghosts in the Machine

episodes.synopsis: Astronema lures the Rangers into a trap on a distant planet.
episodes.title: The Impenetrable Web

episodes.synopsis: The vehicular monster Takenstein stalks the Power Rangers in a vast desert.
episodes.title: A Line in the Sand

episodes.synopsis: Dark Specter's combined armies launch a final all-out assault on the entire universe.
episodes.title: Countdown to Destruction: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: With the forces of evil all but triumphant, the Power Rangers make one last desperate attempt to save Zordon.
episodes.title: Countdown to Destruction: Part 2
